  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"J. L. C. Pompe van Meerdervoort is another teacher who taught photography to Maeda and his fellow students."&lt;SEP&gt;"J. L. C. Pompe van Meerdervoort was a Dutch physician based in Nagasaki during the Bakumatsu period in Japan, teaching medicine, chemistry, and photography."&lt;SEP&gt;"J. L. C. Pompe van Meerdervoort was a physician who taught photography, medicine, and chemistry at Deshima, the Dutch enclave in the harbour of Nagasaki."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1e23935f45bcf7b6a4bc55e10e500a0f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-245f874840849b787c16b7dc50c295cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2580973cbd58d76b61fb1328922f407</data>
</node>
