<node id="&quot;NAGASAKI&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Nagasaki is a city in Japan where Maeda studied photography and assisted Swiss photographer Pierre Rossier."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nagasaki is a city where Kameya Tokujirō and Maeda Genzō studied photography under Jan Karel van den Broek and J. L. C. Pompe van Meerdervoort."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nagasaki is the city where J. L. C. Pompe van Meerdervoort was based and taught at the Nagasaki Naval Training Center."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nagasaki is the city where Kameya Tokujirō and Maeda Genzō studied photography."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1e23935f45bcf7b6a4bc55e10e500a0f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-245f874840849b787c16b7dc50c295cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2580973cbd58d76b61fb1328922f407</data>
