  <data key="d1">"Panosoma brucei is a species of parasitic kinetoplastid belonging to the genus 'Trypanosoma', causing diseases such as African trypanosomiasis or sleeping sickness in humans and animal trypanosomiasis or nagana in animals."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRYPANOSOMA&quot;">
