  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUB-SAHARAN AFRICA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Sub-Saharan Africa is the region south of the Sahara Desert, where the tsetse flies carrying Panosoma brucei are found, transmitting the disease to vertebrates including humans."</data>
