</node>
<node id="&quot;AFRICAN TRYPANOSOMIASIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"African trypanosomiasis, also known as sleeping sickness, is a disease caused by the parasite T. brucei in humans."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ANIMAL TRYPANOSOMIASIS&quot;">
