  <data key="d1">"Animal trypanosomiasis, also known as nagana, is a disease caused by the parasite T. brucei in animals, particularly cattle and horses."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;T. B. BRUCEI&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"T. b. brucei is a subspecies of T. brucei, primarily a parasite of non-human vertebrates and rarely infecting humans."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;T. B. GAMBIENSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"T. b. gambiense is a subspecies of T. brucei, known to be a parasite of humans causing African trypanosomiasis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;T. B. RHODESIENSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"T. b. rhodesiense is a subspecies of T. brucei, also known to be a parasite of humans causing African trypanosomiasis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
