  <data key="d1">"Nagana is a disease caused by the parasite Panosoma brucei in animals, particularly cattle and horses."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NON-HUMAN VERTEBRATES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Non-human vertebrates are animals with a backbone excluding humans, which can be infected by the T. b. brucei subspecies."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HUMAN HISTORY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Human history encompasses the timeline of human civilization and events, including the impact of diseases like African trypanosomiasis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIOLOGICAL AGENT TRANSMISSION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Biological agent transmission refers to the spread of bio-agents through vectors or direct contact, such as the transmission of Panosoma brucei by tsetse flies."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIOLOGICAL WARFARE AGENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Biological warfare agent is a type of bio-agent specifically designed for use in biological warfare, including bacteria, viruses, or toxins."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT RESEARCH&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent research involves studying and developing knowledge about bio-agents, including their properties and potential uses."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT DEVELOPMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent development involves creating and modifying bio-agents for various purposes, including defense and bioterrorism."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT DEPLOYMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent deployment refers to the actual use of bio-agents in bioterrorism or biological warfare."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT CONTAINMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent containment involves measures to prevent the spread of bio-agents and protect against their misuse."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT REGULATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent regulation involves the legal and ethical frameworks governing the use and handling of bio-agents."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT SURVEILLANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent surveillance involves monitoring and detecting the presence of bio-agents to prevent outbreaks or misuse."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT COUNTERMEASURES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent countermeasures involve strategies and technologies to defend against the use of bio-agents in bioterrorism or biological warfare."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT VACCINE DEVELOPMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent vaccine development involves creating vaccines to protect against the effects of bio-agents."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT TREATMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent treatment involves medical interventions to treat individuals exposed to or infected by bio-agents."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT DETECTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent detection involves identifying the presence of bio-agents through diagnostic methods."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT DECONTAMINATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent decontamination involves removing or neutralizing bio-agents from contaminated areas."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT DISPOSAL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent disposal involves safely managing and disposing of bio-agents to prevent environmental contamination."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT STORAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent storage involves securely storing bio-agents to prevent unauthorized access or misuse."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT TRANSPORT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent transport involves moving bio-agents from one location to another, requiring strict security measures."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT LABORATORY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent laboratory is a facility where bio-agents are studied, developed, and handled under controlled conditions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT FIELD TESTING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent field testing involves conducting tests of bio-agents in real-world settings to evaluate their effectiveness."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT SIMULATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent simulation involves using models and scenarios to test and improve responses to potential bio-agent threats."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT TRAINING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent training involves educating personnel on how to handle and respond to bio-agent threats."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT INCIDENT RESPONSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bio-agent incident response involves the actions taken to address and mitigate the effects of a bio-agent incident."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c06647a2b159d0e51d1574ff2452ff3f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BIO-AGENT POLICY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data